<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢唔會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3275cf9ec1eadc524ef9741f9fefd03aa9e24db9","tid":2448020,"uid":84172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你阿媽可以忍佢咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5faf51e203f14ed0d6c52f056ca204c470b991d","tid":2448020,"uid":165817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3275cf9ec1eadc524ef9741f9fefd03aa9e24db9","tid":2448020,"uid":84172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你阿媽可以忍佢咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"我估可能係老一輩好多都係咁<br />\n我媽好細個嗰陣 佢屋企都唔乾淨<br />\n可能已經見慣哂大場面<br />\n<br />\n不過而家佢可能發覺 佢老公有啲青出於藍嘅走勢<br />\n間唔中都會捉我呻<br />\n「我識佢嗰陣佢都唔係咁污糟&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295ef704b8155f7965641647d8f71d9459162909","tid":2448020,"uid":23727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"唉i know that feel arr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母都係好污糟，晚晚喺梳化搣腳皮，搣到成個梳化、成地都係，就算搣到損晒都繼續搣，之後踩到屋企成地都係血跡又唔撚抺，話極佢都唔改。<br />\n<br />\n佢乜撚嘢都可以擺上飯枱，出完街啲衫褲、手袋、有次連隻狗屙完尿嘅狗尿片都可以擺上飯枱。<br />\n<br />\n講起飯枱，佢條抺布可以乜撚都抺，抺下枱又抺下地再抺下嘴，話佢佢就會話覺得自己塊布好乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企口罩亂咁放，周圍晾，幾日先換個口罩呢啲就基本嘢啦。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係，佢係真心地覺得自己係最乾淨嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b32fa7b572b639252d1b932b490